  "body": "In the last step of the [tutorial](http://facebook.github.io/react/docs/tutorial.html) where optimistic updates are added, I believe there is a race condition if the following occurs:\n1. `loadCommentsFromServer` called by `setInterval`.  ajax GET call started.\n2. `handleCommentSubmit` called adding new comment to `CommentBox`'s state. ajax POST call started.\n3. ajax call by `loadCommentsFromServer` returns with stale data.\n4. ajax call by `handleCommentSubmit` returns with new data.\n5. `loadCommentsFromServer` called by `setInterval`.  ajax GET call started.\n\nThis will result in `initial_comments -> new_comments -> initial_comments -> new_comments`  being seen by user.\n",
